results.title: Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #642
results.description: ORIGIN OF THE SPECIES PART 1 When Norman Osborn's baby is born, every villain on the planet wants the first ever strain of pure Goblin blood, leaving Spider-Man's friends and family exposed to a sinister plan...

results.title: Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #643
results.description: ORIGIN OF THE SPECIES PART 2 Can Spidey hold off his greatest foes and keep the Osborn baby safe?

results.title: Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #644
results.description: ORIGIN OF THE SPECIES PART 3 First, Spider-Man fights The Vulture. Then, The Rhino! The race for the Osborn offspring continues!

results.title: Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #645
results.description: ORIGIN OF THE SPECIES PART 4 Everyone's favorite friendly neighborhood Spider-Man isn't so friendly tonight. No one knows that better than the criminals he's been taking down. Featuring Shocker, Chameleon and Doc Ock!

results.title: Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #646
results.description: ORIGIN OF THE SPECIES CONCLUSION The final showdown is here! Who will claim the Osborn baby?

results.title: Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #647
results.description: BRAND NEW DAY is over! While recent events may have drastically changed Peter and his friends, the ol' Parker luck is still around...

results.title: Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #649
results.description: The Hobgoblin's back! And he's ready to hit the BIG TIME too - with a whole new bag of tricks! Who's under the mask this time? Is it Roderick Kingsley, Jason Macendale, or somebody else?

results.title: Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #650
results.description: To face off against an amped-up Hobgoblin, you need an amped-up Spider-Man! What's the story behind Spidey's new suit? What is it and what can it do?
